Run the Tempest at environment with creating all the needed entities (users, tenants, flavors, images, networks).

1. Dependencies (actual for the Tempest Grizzly)

1.1. Ubuntu 12.04

python-dev python-virtualenv libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev libmysqlclient-dev libpq-dev git-core expect

1.1.1 Ubuntu 13.04

bffi-dev

1.2. CentOS 6.4

python-devel python-virtualenv libxml2-devel libxslt-devel mysql-devel mysql-client mysql-shared gcc openssl-devel postgresql-devel git-core expect


~/.ssh/config
Host *
    StrictHostKeyChecking no
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null
